data.meta_description:
7,197 likes, 34 comments - freeda_en on May 20, 2024: "Today is Cher’s birthday. She was born 20 May 1946.
Cher’s 1996 interview for Dateline NBC’s Jane Pauley garnered the singer-actress much publicity. In it, Cher tells the story of her mother asking her to “settle down and marry a rich man”, to which Cher replied, “Mom, I am a rich man.”
We love you Cher, and happy birthday!
